==National Cup==
{{AFL Haw}} defeated {{AFL Nor}} 14.19 (103) to 7.12 (54). (For an explanation of scoring see [[Australian rules football]]).
==Premiership Season== Due to the addition of the [[Adelaide Football Club|Adelaide Crows]], the number of teams in the competition was uneven. Therefore each team had 2 byes for the season; 7 teams had a bye in Round 1, and then each succeding week 1 team had a bye. In total each team would play 22 games for the season.
